BTTAdditionalActions.BTTPredefinedActionName: Close currently open Touch Bar group
Close currently open Touch Bar group

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set temp to do shell script "/usr/local/bin/istats cpu --value-only | awk '{print int($1+0.5)}'"set value to do shell script "sed s/[a-zA-Z:{},]//g <<< " & temp# set value to "CPU " & valueset value to value & "°C"return value

set temp to do shell script "/usr/local/bin/istats scan TCGC --value-only | awk '{print int($1+0.5)}'"set value to do shell script "sed s/[a-zA-Z:{},]//g <<< " & temp# set value to "GPU " & valueset value to value & "°C"return value

# Get fan RPM(s) and clean up outputset value to do shell script "/usr/local/bin/istats fan --value-only | tail -n +2 | tr '
' ' '| tr -s ' '"set value to value & "RPM"return value
